Ledger Nano S test reporter

1, Buy Ledger Nano S
   1) Must Buy Ledger From https://www.ledger.com/
   2) https://shop.ledger.com/products/ledger-nano-s
   3) https://shop.ledger.com/pages/supported-crypto-assets

2, Download ledger-live
   1) https://shop.ledger.com/pages/ledger-live
   2) https://download-live.ledger.com/releases/latest/download/linux

3,  AppImage
  1) https://appimage.org/
 运行一个Appimage应用，如此简单:
给予它运行权限
$ chmod a+x Subsurface*.AppImage
然后直接运行！
$ ./Subsurface*.AppImage
非常简单，不是吗？ 

